{
  "stem": "3380.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, why do you have to have that number?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Why do you have to look at it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Why should this be a reminder?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You will remember this thing anyhow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the surgeon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, let me take it off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, I used to play with Jack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jack was a baby at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jack was a baby at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to pull the hair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was fascinated by the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I decided, if he want to take it off-- I remember he just took it off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Took him about a half an hour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He cut it, cut it out, [? they ?] [? meet, ?] and put [? the ?] [? meet ?] back together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said that it's gone for good and forever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I realize now I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, because today we got four consecutive numbers, three here in-- in the city of Chicago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's fantastic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I removed my number, but I got people one number above me and one number ahead of me and below.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this guy, what got a number above my brother's name, he-- his name was not-- he lives in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shantovsky ?] with a K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he had a friend, what his name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tensir. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he changed his name from K, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shantovksy ?] to [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chintovksy ?] to be with him together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Usually, we liked-- this-- that friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's the reason he got one number ahead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, he was not entitled for that number.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I remember the way he pushed himself in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't want to stay with them together.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
